## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **nirsevimab Beyfortus 2023** = first long-acting RSV prefusion-F mAb 영아 single-dose seasonal prophylaxis. palivizumab Synagis monthly era 종료. quantum-VQE 의 prefusion-F antigen + Fc-extended IgG1-YTE 모두 직접 fit.
2. **abrysvo (Pfizer) + arexvy (GSK) 2023** = maternal RSV vaccine 32-36주 임신부 — passive 영아 보호 6mo. cross-vaccinology + cross-women_obgyn paradigm shift.
3. **buprenorphine NOWS** = 2020s shorter LOS vs morphine (BBORN trial). methadone/morphine/clonidine classical 패러다임 부분 shift. eat-sleep-console (ESC) non-pharmacologic 가 ESC trial 2023 first-line — 약물 사용 ↓.
4. **TXA WOMAN trial 2017 → 2020 PPH 1g IV** = 산후 출혈 mortality reduction 1.5h-window. cross-emergency_medicine + obstetric 통합. 단순 antifibrinolytic 으로 maternal mortality intervention.
5. **carbetocin (Pabal/Duratocin) EU 2007 — heat-stable formulation WHO 2019** = oxytocin 의 heat-stable LA 대안. LMIC cold-chain 부족 환경 PPH 예방.
6. **therapeutic hypothermia 33-34°C × 72h (TOBY/CoolCap 2010s)** = HIE 신경보호 표준. 약물 X 절차 X. 하지만 어떻게 cooling 이 mitochondrial/excitotoxic 기전을 modulate 하는지 quantum-VQE 가 indirect 만 가능.
7. **caffeine citrate Cafcit (CAP trial 2007)** = 미숙아 무호흡 + BPD 예방 표준. aminophylline/theophylline 에서 paradigm shift. cheap + safe.
8. **anti-VEGF ROP (BEAT-ROP 2011 / RAINBOW 2018)** = laser ablation 의 alternative. bevacizumab/ranibizumab intravitreal — cross-sensory + ophthalmology 직접. 시스템 흡수 + neurodevelopmental long-term concern open.
9. **synthetic surfactant lacking SP-B/C historical fail (Exosurf 1990s 시장 퇴장)** = 동물-derived (Curosurf/Survanta/Infasurf) 우월. recombinant SP-B/C + 합성 lipid hybrid 가 next-gen. quantum-VQE 의 SP-B/C 펩티드 lipid-bilayer 안정성 + interfacial 활성 prediction 핵심.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, NICU + maternal-fetal 임상 의미 한정 + IRB pediatric/perinatal extreme 제약.

